
1- create venv
2- install django
3- startproject bookstore
4- create the following in this project
    1- page contact us --> any data
    2- aboutus  ---> any data
    3- bookindex ==> display books in a table
        book {id , title, author , no_of_pages, image , price}

       when you click show --> on specific book
       redirect to new page
       display book details in a card
       https://getbootstrap.com/docs/5.3/components/card/#about

general notes
   1- use url include files
   2- use urlnames
   3- all pages must have the same navbar
   4- you must use django templates directives


